# Title

Don't Mention Your Dead Ponies

# Type

45 minute talk

# Abstract

In this 45 minutes I will talk about my experience of starting a community from zero, I will mention strategies, give out tools to help you better organize, grow and present your communities. There will be some stand-up comedy tips and jedi tricks

# Story

I was invited to GDG Summit in 2018, to talk about my experience with GDG Lisbon, I prepared the talk focused on GDGs but later it grew to be something more general, something more personal from my experience.
